<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to KTBlog!</title>
  <!--[if mso]>
  <noscript>
    <xml>
      <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
      </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
    </xml>
  </noscript>
  <![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f6f9;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f6f9;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E4DB7 0%, #3B6FD4 100%); padding: 40px 40px 30px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">KTBlog</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 24px; color: #1a1a2e; text-align: center;">Welcome to KTBlog!</h2>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">Hello {{name}},</p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">We're thrilled to have you join the KTBlog community! Your account has been successfully created and you're ready to explore everything we have to offer.</p>

              <!-- Highlight Banner -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E4DB7 0%, #3B6FD4 100%); padding: 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff;">Your Journey Starts Here</h3>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); font-size: 14px;">Discover insightful articles, premium content, and a vibrant community.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Features -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f8f9fb; border-radius: 8px; margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 24px;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; color: #1a1a2e;">What You Can Do Now:</h3>
                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                      <tr><td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Read insightful articles from top writers</td></tr>
                      <tr><td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Bookmark your favorite posts for later</td></tr>
                      <tr><td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Join discussions in the comments</td></tr>
                      <tr><td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Subscribe for premium content access</td></tr>
                      <tr><td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Customize your reading preferences</td></tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- CTA Buttons -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 32px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #1E4DB7; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin-right: 8px;">Go to Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #6b7280; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Login</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">If you have any questions or need assistance getting started, our support team is always here to help.</p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">Welcome aboard!</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a2e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">The KTBlog Team</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">&copy; {{year}} KTBlog. All rights reserved.</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #1E4DB7; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
